lead_paragraph: Desperate for a quarterback, Justin Fuente heard of Paxton Lynch thanks to a note an administrator left on the new Memphis coach's desk.

headline.print_headline: NFL DRAFT: Lynch Could Be Highest QB Drafted From Memphis
